## Part 3 тАФ Security Tab (Make Functional + New Features)

### Current State
The Security tab is **entirely cosmetic** тАФ all settings are local React state:
- 2FA toggle тЖТ does nothing
- Session timeout input тЖТ does nothing
- Audit logging toggle тЖТ does nothing (audit logging is always on)

The backend has: rate limiting (`10/min` on login), JWT tokens (24h fixed expiry), token blacklisting on logout, password validation (8+ chars, upper/lower/digit). **No 2FA exists.**

### 3A тАФ Two-Factor Authentication (Email/SMS OTP)

#### [MODIFY] [models.py](file:///c:/Users/pc/Documents/Github/server/app/models.py)

Add fields to [User](file:///c:/Users/pc/Documents/Github/server/app/models.py#131-232) model:
```python
# 2FA fields
otp_secret = db.Column(db.String(32), nullable=True)     # For TOTP/random OTP generation
otp_enabled = db.Column(db.Boolean, default=False)        # Whether 2FA is active for this user
otp_method = db.Column(db.String(10), nullable=True)      # "email" or "sms"
```

#### [NEW] [otp_service.py](file:///c:/Users/pc/Documents/Github/server/app/services/otp_service.py)

Lightweight OTP service using Python's `secrets` module (no external deps):
- `generate_otp(user)` тЖТ generates 6-digit code, stores hashed in a temporary cache (Redis-free: use a simple DB table or in-memory dict with TTL)
- `verify_otp(user, code)` тЖТ validates code within 5-minute window
- `send_otp(user)` тЖТ dispatches OTP via [_send_email()](file:///c:/Users/pc/Documents/Github/server/app/services/notification_service.py#87-116) or [_send_sms()](file:///c:/Users/pc/Documents/Github/server/app/services/notification_service.py#122-142) based on `user.otp_method`

#### [MODIFY] [auth_controller.py](file:///c:/Users/pc/Documents/Github/server/app/controllers/auth_controller.py)

Change login flow to support 2FA:
1. First step: validate credentials тЖТ if 2FA enabled, return `{ requires2FA: true, tempToken: "..." }` instead of final JWT
2. New endpoint `POST /auth/verify-otp` тЖТ accepts `{ tempToken, code }` тЖТ returns real JWT

| Method | Endpoint | Purpose |
|--------|----------|---------|
| `POST` | `/auth/verify-otp` | Verify OTP code and complete login |

#### [MODIFY] Frontend login flow

Update the login page to handle the `requires2FA` response тАФ show an OTP input screen before completing authentication.

